      <div class="msgContentFrame">Using Absorb DEF is not just about giving yourself higher def, in fact in a party situation that isnt much use at all. However as a debuff on the mob I can say that if it lands it makes a significant difference in lowering the defence of the mob which is very usefull. I have not experimented with the other absorb spells yet as I'm still fairly low level but I would imagine they are all usefull on certain mobs. During beta I thought these spells were pretty useless, but as with many things THM my views have changed or are changing.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="HTTP://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=2993179" rel="external nofollow" title="lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=2993179">Loadstone Profile</a> <br /><a href="HTTP://ffxiv.zam.com/forum.html?forum=179&amp;mid=1282291867193441649" rel="external" title="ffxiv.zam.com/forum.html?forum=179&amp;mid=1282291867193441649">Thaumaturge Guide</a> <br /> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1229110.png" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
