      <div class="msgContentFrame">I haven't got figures to back this up, but I have used this spell for solo purposes and the damage the mobs hit you for is reduced, I am certain of this. PIE may be the factor in this spell hitting. If the spell is successful you will see the icon appear on the mob and yourself. If the icon does not appear then the spell failed. Unlike Siphon MP for example, this spell is not 100% by any means and in my current setup I hit the mobs I am fighting (Island crab vs party of 5) around 30% of the time - the spell doesnt last a great amount of time though, I would guess around 30-40 seconds at best. Maybe increasing INT may extend this but I don't know and haven't had the chance to check as of yet.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="HTTP://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=2993179" rel="external nofollow" title="lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=2993179">Loadstone Profile</a> <br /><a href="HTTP://ffxiv.zam.com/forum.html?forum=179&amp;mid=1282291867193441649" rel="external" title="ffxiv.zam.com/forum.html?forum=179&amp;mid=1282291867193441649">Thaumaturge Guide</a> <br /> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1229110.png" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
